        "Mind Shadows is a revolutionary platform that is designed to help people identify their own mental health issues and get support. <br />
        Thanks to a user-friendly interface, users can use self-testing tools and surveys to specifically assess their mental health.<br />
        This platform provides personalized advice and connects users to mental health services, self-care tips, <br />and professional
