                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/MS11.jpg" class="d-block w-100 slide-img-item " alt="ggggg">

                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size: 40px; color: black; font-weight: bold; font-style: oblique ">
                        "THERE ARE WOUNDS THAT NEVER SHOW ON THE BODY THAT ARE DEEPER AND MORE HURTFUL THAN ANYTHING THAT BLEEDS"
                        </h5>
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/MS8.jpeg" class="d-block w-100 slide-img-item" alt="...">

                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size:40px; color:black; font-weight:bold; font-style:oblique">
                        "REMEMBER THAT YOUR MENTAL HEALTH IS PRIORITY, YOUR INNER PEACE IS ESSENTIAL AND YOUR SELF CARE IS NECESSITY"
                        </h5>
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/MS13.jpeg"  class="d-block w-100 slide-img-item" alt="...">

                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size:40px; color:black; font-weight:bold; font-style:oblique">
                        "DAILY MEDITATION IS THE ANTIDOTE TO WORRIES ,STRESS AND NONSTOP THINKING WHICH DISTURB FOCUS AND TRANQUILITY AND WASTE MENTAL ENERGY"
                        </h5>
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/MS12.jpg" class="d-block w-100 slide-img-item" alt="...">

                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size:40px; color:black; font-weight:bold; font-style:oblique">
                        "TO KEEP THE BODY IN GOOD HEALTH IS A DUTY OTHERWISE WE SHALL NOT BE ABLE TO KEEP OUR MIND STRONG AND CLEAR"
                        </h5>
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Content/img/MS14.jpg" class="d-block w-100 slide-img-item" alt="...">

