    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-doctor fs-1"></i>
                    <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Consult a Specialist", "index", "Home", new {area="" }, new {@class="text-decoration-none, text-reset ", @id="consult-item"}) </h3>
                    <script>
                        let clickBtn = document.getElementById('consult-item')
                        clickBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                            alert("for consult a specialist ...Please Register at First, If you have already register then  login to consult a Specialist.Thank You")
                        })
                    </script>
                    <span class="text-item">
                        "Users can seamlessly connect with a diverse 
                        network of mental health professionals
                        including psychiatrists, therapists, and  
                        psychologists. Through our platform, this 
                        connection is facilitated efficiently, 
                        guaranteeing users receive prompt, personalized 
                        support."
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse fs-1"></i>
                    <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Mental Health Tips", "MentalTips", "Home", new {area=" " }, new {@class="text-decoration-none, text-reset"})</h3>
                    <span class="text-item">
                        "An array of self-care holistic practices like yoga,
                        art therapy,  journaling, binaural music,
                        nutritional guidance, etc. By incorporating 
                        these strategies into their daily routines, 
                        users can effectively manage their mental health, 
                        ultimately improving their overall health and 
                        fostering a sense of balance and resilience."
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-notes-medical fs-1"></i>
                    <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Take Self-Assessment Tests", "index", "Home", new { area = "" }, new { @class = "text-decoration-none, text-reset ", @id = "self-assessment-item" }) </h3>
                    <script>
                        let clickBtn2 = document.getElementById('self-assessment-item')
                        clickBtn2.addEventListener('click', () => {
                            alert("for Take a Self-Assessment Test ...Please Register at First, If you have already register then  login to Take a Self Assesest. Thank You")
                        })
                    </script>
                    <span class="text-item">
                        "Take a self-assessment test backed by research
                        to identify mental well-being. Through these
                        tests, individuals can promptly recognize
                        their mental health status and take necessary
                        actions for improvement."
                    </span>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="d-flex flex-row mb-3 mt-3 blog-item-none">
            <div class="p-2 info-contain">
                <h3 style="text-align:center;
                    font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                    ">
                    Redefining Normalcy in Mental Health
                </h3>
                <center>
                    <img class="img-fluid " style="width:350px;height:180px; border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0px 0px 10px 0px" src="~/Content/img/ment1.jpg" />
                </center>
                <p style="text-align:justify;">
                    It can be tough… but you’re not alone!

                    Let's redefine normalcy, celebrating diversity and
                    individuality while respecting each person's
                    journey to mental well-being.
                    In a world of diverse experiences,
                    the concept of "normal" is subjective.
                    Society's standards evolve, and what's
                    considered unconventional today may be
                    celebrated tomorrow. Embracing our quirks
                    is vital, as they define our uniqueness.
                    However, if any trait poses a threat or
                    disrupts life, seeking help is crucial.
                    Self-acceptance and appreciation of
                    differences foster a more inclusive society.
                    However, if any trait poses a threat or
                    disrupts life, seeking help is crucial.
                    Self-acceptance and appreciation of
                    differences foster a more inclusive society.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 info-contain3">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;
                    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                    ">
                    Empowering Indian Youth's Mental Health
                </h3>
                <center>
                    <img class="img-fluid" style="width:350px;height:180px; border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0px 0px 10px 0px" src="~/Content/img/ment2.jpg" />
                </center>
                <p style="text-align:justify;">
                    In many Indian households, discussions about mental
                    health are often brushed aside or overlooked,
                    particularly among parents who may not fully
                    understand its importance. This trend is especially
                    prevalent among Indian youth, who may find themselves
                    in a challenging position when it comes to seeking support.
                    Many are under 18 years old or lack financial independence,
                    making it necessary to rely on their parents or guardians for assistance.

                    Our platform addresses this critical gap by providing a
                    safe and supportive space to openly discuss their
                    mental health concerns. Here, they can find
                    understanding and acceptance, free from judgment
                    or shame. Additionally, our platform offers
                    expert guidance and resources tailored to
                    the unique challenges faced by Indian youth,
                    empowering them to navigate their mental
                    health journeys with confidence.</p>
            </div>

        </div>


        <div class="d-flex ">
            <div class="p-2 info-contain5">
                <h3> Unveiling Unspoken Mental Health Topics for Young Adults</h3>
               <center>
                   <img style="border-radius:10px" class="img-fluid info-img" src="~/Content/img/ment3.jpg" />
               </center>
                
                <p>
                    By shedding light on unspoken topics yet very common, 
                    we aim to foster understanding and support for young 
                    adults navigating their mental health journeys.
                    Generalized anxiety disorder and hyper-independence can
                    hinder daily functioning and overall well-being.
                    Self-harm, a prevalent yet overlooked coping mechanism, 
                    alleviates emotional pain for many young adults. 
                    Intrusive thoughts, persistent and distressing, 
                    disrupt lives with unwanted sensations.
                    Depression's stigma and the common phenomenon 
                    of masking further complicate matters.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 info-contain7 ">
                <h3>Stay Informed</h3>
                <center>
                    <img class="img-fluid" style="width:450px;height:250px;border-radius:10px;" src="~/Content/img/ment4.jpg" />
                </center>
                <p>
                    Your Guide to Mental Well-Being and Self-Improvement
                    Whether you're seeking self-improvement strategies or
                    want to stay informed about mental health trends, our 
                    blog is your go-to resource for holistic well-being.
                    Prioritize your mental and physical health journey
                    with our comprehensive and insightful content
                    Learn effective stress management techniques, 
                    mindfulness practices, and resilience-building 
                    exercises to enhance mental health. Discover the 
                    importance of proper nutrition and supplements 
                    for overall vitality. Empower yourself with expert 
                    advice and practical tips to thrive mentally and 
                    emotionally.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="container mt-3">
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users fs-1"></i>
                    <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Lived Experience", "LivedExperience", "Home", new { area = " " }, new { @class = "text-decoration-none, text-reset" })</h3>
                    <span class="text-item">
                        "Take a glimpse into the lives of individuals
                        with mental illness their challenges,
                        victories, and journeys to overcome adversity.
                        By sharing their experiences, we aim to
                        create a sense of solidarity and comfort
