                        conversations, individuals find support and
                        encouragement, building meaningful connections
                        that contribute to their mental well-being."
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star fs-1"></i>
                    <h3>@Html.ActionLink("Send FeedBack", "Feedback", "User", new { area = " " }, new { @class = "text-decoration-none, text-reset" })</h3>
                    <span class="text-item">
                        "User reviews on mental health resources,
                        therapies, and services offer valuable
                        insights and recommendations. They
                        contribute to a supportive community,
                        aiding others in making informed decisions
                        about their mental health journey."
                    </span>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

</main>